{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/tech/2020/02/26/WSL安装ruby环境.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6e2f3298-8c37-5c9e-88c1-5e8ddcdf53de","excerpt":"WSL 安装 ruby 环境 虽然我这个博客是基于 jekyll 的，但是因为国内整 ruby 的环境实在痛苦，但是最近不得不又重新搞起来了，只能在这里记录一下。 首先安装环境 然后修改 gem 的环境变量 修改 source 为 ruby-china 接着安装 jekyll 即可","html":"<h1>WSL 安装 ruby 环境</h1>\n<p>虽然我这个博客是基于 jekyll 的，但是因为国内整 ruby 的环境实在痛苦，但是最近不得不又重新搞起来了，只能在这里记录一下。</p>\n<p>首先安装环境</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">sudo</span> <span class=\"token function\">apt</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> ruby ruby-dev build-essential</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>然后修改 gem 的环境变量</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\">GEM_HOME</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/gems\n<span class=\"token builtin class-name\">export</span> <span class=\"token assign-left variable\"><span class=\"token environment constant\">PATH</span></span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token environment constant\">$HOME</span>/gems/bin:<span class=\"token environment constant\">$PATH</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>修改 source 为 ruby-china</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">gem sources --add https://gems.ruby-china.com/ --remove https://rubygems.org/</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>接着安装 jekyll 即可</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">gem <span class=\"token function\">install</span> jekyll bundler</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"category":"tech"},"fields":{"slug":"/tech/2020/02/26/WSL安装ruby环境.html","date":"February 26, 2020","title":"WSL安装ruby环境"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/tech/2020/02/26/WSL安装ruby环境.html","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/02/25/使用stryker做mutation test.html","title":"使用stryker做mutation test"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/fe/2020/02/27/使用rust和webassembly开发game_of_life.html","title":"使用rust和webassembly开发game_of_life"},"frontmatter":{"category":"fe"}}}}}